Air Freight Services

Freight services by TrueLog ensure reliable and efficient air freight solutions for your international shipping needs.

  1. Home

Air Freight

Truelog's air freight services are designed to provide swift and efficient transportation solutions for your cargo, ensuring timely delivery to destinations across the globe. With access to 90% of the world's countries through insured and compliant agreements with various airlines, Truelog guarantees reserved space and expedited delivery for your shipments.

Email us on

sales@truelog.com.sg

WhatsApp Custom Enquires

+65 9771 8172

Give us a call on

+65 6909 3756

Tailored Air Freight Services

  • Time-Sensitive Shipments When time is of the essence and your goods require expedited delivery, TrueLog offers air transportation solutions to meet your urgent deadlines.
  • Comprehensive Coverage Whether you're importing, exporting, or transhipping, TrueLog facilitates seamless air freight operations with full visibility and control over your cargo.
  • Door-to-Door Services Enjoy hassle-free transportation with TrueLog's door-to-door services, including IOR, EOR and DDP arrangements, ensuring smooth clearance and delivery of goods to your customer at any time.
  • Real-Time Tracking Track your shipments in real-time with TrueLog's advanced tracking system, providing you with up-to-date information on the status and location of your cargo throughout its journey.

What We Offer

Industry-Specific Solutions

TrueLog offers comprehensive logistics solutions tailored to your specific needs. From sensitive equipment to project cargo, we provide expert handling and transportation services worldwide.

Sensitive Equipment

Specialized handling and transportation solutions for delicate and sensitive equipment, minimizing the risk of damage during transit.

Project Cargo

Expert handling of complex project cargo, including oversized or heavy cargo, ensuring seamless execution and timely delivery.

Special Services

Sea-Air: Combined air and sea service offering cost-effectiveness with faster lead times than ocean freight.
Air-Land: Combined air and truck service for swift transportation to or from an inland destination.

With TrueLog’s air freight forwarding services, you can trust in our expertise and global network to deliver your cargo safely and efficiently to its destination. Contact us today for customized air freight solutions tailored to your business needs.
